source: crates/daemon/tests/cli_help.rs
expression: stdout
---
Classify search results as ACTION/FYI/ROUTINE using the cached summarizer verdict

Usage: mxr triage [OPTIONS] <QUERY>

Arguments:
  <QUERY>

Options:
      --account <ACCOUNT>
      --format <FORMAT>    [possible values: table, json, jsonl, csv, ids]
      --limit <LIMIT>      [default: 50]
      --mode <MODE>        [possible values: lexical, hybrid, semantic]
      --sort <SORT>        [possible values: date, verdict]
      --verdict <VERDICT>  [possible values: action, fyi, routine]
  -h, --help               Print help
